sources.title: The Brink Of Extinction | Full Action Movie | Post Apocalyptic Survival
sources.description:
Fifteen years have passed since the devastating events of World War III, and while the nuclear winter has finally lifted, humanity teeters on the brink of extinction. With the remnants of civilization shattered, survival has become a daily struggle where food is a rare commodity. In this harsh new world, most people resort to desperate measures, resorting to theft and violence just to stay alive.
2020.  Stars: Luke Hobson, Georgie Smibert, Chris Kaye
